パッケージ ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.ast.java

クラス JavaMethodBodyConverter

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.jdt.internal.compiler.ASTVisitor
ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.ast.java.JavaMethodBodyConverter
public class JavaMethodBodyConverter
extends org.eclipse.jdt.internal.compiler.ASTVisitor
Visitor to generate an intermediate tree (general, rooted, labeled, valued tree) out of a method body.
作成者:
Beat Fluri, Giacomo Ghezzi
